txt.en: 'You should bring this note to Thane Ordlac at once. It contains information that he must see.\n\n'Do not delay!'

'Greetings, [placeholder]! How goes your hunt? You found another note? Let me see it.

'Ha! These brutes think to murder my wife within my very home! These half-orcs were careless indeed to be carrying these orders upon their persons.

'Well, we shall take advantage of this, to be sure....'
The note you found upon the leaders of the half-orcs seemed to distress Cenulf.
Bring the note you found to Ordlac
Thane Ordlac is in the Mead Hall of Oserley.\n\nCenulf told you to bring the note you found to Thane Ordlac at once.
